I'm a bit busy getting our first
user set up with the app but

00:01:44.380 --> 00:01:45.990
the developer has some free time.

00:01:45.990 --> 00:01:47.860
Maybe they could join you.

00:01:47.860 --> 00:01:49.010
&gt;&gt; Sure.
That'd be great.

